snippet.title: Task-Force 9 trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the ultimate stealth and tactical shooter experience with Task-Force 9! This upcoming game puts you in the shoes of a highly-skilled operative, As part of a global anti-terrorist unit.
hone your special awareness with urban fighting mixed with stealth, coming soon the Steam and the Quest 2.
Discord: https://discord.gg/gGYDPZsmVN
